title: Castle Rock S1E10 Explained + Ending!
author: Think Story
comment: Anyone notice young henry retracing his steps in the snow was a nod to the shining when Danny did the same thing in the maze to trick his own crazy father.
When young Henry retraces his steps in the snow to fool his dad...it's the same trick Danny Torrence uses in the Shinning to escape his father in the maze.
One thing that's nagging me: Why did Lacey tell the kid to ask for Henry Matthew Deaver? That's a pretty major plot point that never gets referenced.
Big thanks from my wife and I. Was were struggling to tie all the loose ends and your video helped a lot.

A commenter on another channel said they thought that Henry was going to shoot at The Kid in the forest right when the schisma takes him back and the bullet would end up shooting Molly in the other timeline. I thought that would've been an interesting ending.
description:
I delve into the season finale, episode ten of Castle Rock "Romans" and look at the hidden details, mysteries, easter eggs and Stephen King references.
